{"tid":2079692,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"黃翠如否認整容 天生「虎鼻」唔使整","createTime":"2020-06-26T03:01:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-26T04:13:50.000Z","uid":137088,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"0d10590599de052d8d4a1416d72ab9762a6b6834","tid":2079692,"uid":137088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T03:01:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200624/photo/bkn-20200624172455310-0624_00862_001_01p.jpg?20200624180532\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200624%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200624172455310-0624_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20200624180532&h=0d195e07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而講到翠如被傳整容整到「木偶鼻」，又與好姊妹唐詩詠一起整容，她即否認：「我從來都唔係行鬥靚嘅路線，大家可以睇番我以前有線嘅節目，同埋我最靚就係個鼻，媽咪由細到大都讚我係『虎鼻』，有福氣，我100%冇心虛答你哋，我一定唔會郁我個鼻，唔好屈我！」問到可會整其他地方？她笑言：「其他地方老咗我唔敢包。（因為呢件事好嬲？）冇嘅，我喺負面新聞下長大。（當幫劇集宣傳？）ok啦，都唔係第一次。」而Shiga亦幫口，表示翠如不貪靚，她曾為對方介紹facial，但對方一年都未去做。<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.viralcham.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/%E9%BB%84%E7%BF%A0%E5%A6%82%E8%BF%9B%E5%8C%96%E5%8F%B2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.viralcham.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F04%2F%25E9%25BB%2584%25E7%25BF%25A0%25E5%25A6%2582%25E8%25BF%259B%25E5%258C%2596%25E5%258F%25B2.png&h=7ea089ae&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"79fd3af490f59628125d03fa141efa8a213c05c7","tid":2079692,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T03:04:56.000Z","msg":"徐若瑄?"},{"pid":"3b155746daf1fc5fd59f8a0498f9146651508dce","tid":2079692,"uid":279981,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T03:08:15.000Z","msg":"TVB害人不淺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n還我有線翠魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"739cc2a50e9ccbe854cec4ee6e2ee80f7d252873","